            <li> • Real-time Tracking - Track the current status of <br> your complaint anytime. </li> <br><br>
            <li> • Notifications & Updates - Get automatic updates <br> on complaint progress. </li> <br><br>
            <li> • Admin Dashboard - Allows administrators to <br> manage and resolve complaints efficiently. </li> <br><br>
            <li> • History Records - Maintain a digital record of all <br> previous complaints for future reference. </li>
